                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pourquoilou/">噜</a>
                    <span>2011-06-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">虽然仍未摆脱内部权力斗争的说法，但是拿出了很多党内文件</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="385634748">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-385634748" class="vote-count">0</span>
